  'eea0b445-6b85-4d67-8e52-b8792cd7883f',
  '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001',
  $escape$nmap - Post-Exploitation Essentials$escape$,
  $escape$To perform post-exploitation tasks with nmap, utilize the -script argument to execute specific scripts. For privilege escalation, run `nmap -script=ms17-010` to exploit the EternalBlue vulnerability. Lateral movement can be achieved with `nmap -script=shiva` to scan for open shares. For persistence, use `nmap -script=windows/smbrelayx.py` to establish a persistent connection.$escape$,
  NULL,
  NULL,
